creator: Verto Group
descriptionHtml:
Find, connect and engage with your local church easily with the Church Central App.

With the Church Central app you can set your church as your home church for quick and easy access to all the latest content and features:

• Search and stream sermons
• Check out the prayer wall and submit your own prayer requests publicly or privately.
• Receive updates and info by push notifications.
• Create an account with the church to receive information and notifications tailored to you.
• Stay connected with the latest events, with one-click add to calendar functionality.
• Get directions to events
• Connect with church staff and leadership.
• Stay up to date with the latest news and announcements.
• Add church content to your favourites so you can revisit it at a later date.
• Share content straight to your social media.
• Search all your church content with the easy keyword search tool.

Church Central is a central resource where you can search to find churches by name, ministry, suburb or by map with the quick and easy ‘Around Me’ or ‘Search this Area’ function.

You can also search and stream sermons across all Australian Church Central churches by topic, speaker and more.

Church Central is a powerful and passionate app for Australian Churches.

Download it and start engaging today.

Keen to have your church included? Visit us at www.churchcentral.com.au to get in touch.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
• A range of performance improvements and general housekeeping to make your app experience even better
• Added support for Android 10

title: Church Central

creator: Verto Group
descriptionHtml:
A powerful Aussie app resource to connect and engage with your local church community.

In the app you can:
• Save your local church to your favourites to access all their latest content and notifications.
• Receive the latest updates, content, and info by push notifications
• Watch or listen to the latest sermon anywhere, anytime and you can even write sermon notes within the app
• Stay connected with the latest events, register your attendance, and get directions on how to get there
• Check out the latest news and announcements
• Donate
• Know what to pray for with the prayer wall and even submit your own request publicly or privately
• Create an account and login to receive more personalised content
• Search for any content with the useful keyword search tool

To get started:
• Select ‘Find a Church’
• Search by name, keyword or via the interactive map
• Select the church and add to favourites.
• The app will launch directly to your favourited church

In the Church Central app, you can also search our library of Australian sermons by topic, speaker or by church.

Keen to have your local church included? Visit us at www.churchcentral.co to get in touch.

Verto Group are an Australian software company passionately supporting local churches with our suite of digital communication solutions including app, web and donations.

Built, managed and supported by us…. right here in Australia!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
This update includes the functionality to link directly to google maps for directions when selecting an event or church location.

We have also included a small number of performance improvements and minor display fixes.

More updates will come as we continue to release new features.

Thank you for all the positive feedback on the recent app upgrade.

The Verto Team
